com.sds.iot.sdk

Class IotClientConfig

  • Object
    • com.sds.iot.sdk.IotClientConfig

  • public class IotClientConfig
extends Object
    이 클래스는 biot 라이브러리의 기본값을 제공합니다. 여기에 정의된 값은 IotClient를 통해 런타임에 재정의 할 수 있습니다.

        public void setEncType(String encType)
        Encryption type. default '0'.
      • 0 : None
      • 1 : DH_AES256(Deprecated)
      • 2 : SEAL(Unsupported)
      • 3 : ITA_AES128
      • 4 : WBC(Unsupported)
      • 5 : ITA_AES256(Unsupported)

  • getCompressUseBytes

  • setCompressUseBytes

    public void setCompressUseBytes(int compressUseBytes)
    Minimum data bytes to compress. default '0'. (Note: Data is compressed when sending message. But auth and keep-alive messages will NOT be compressed regardless of this config.) e.g. if compressUseBytes=0, No compression. if compressUseBytes=1, All message data will be compressed. if compressUseBytes=1048576, Message data greater than 1MB will be compressed. if compressUseBytes greater than N, Message data greater than N bytes will be compressed.
    Parameters:
    compressUseBytes - 압축 크기
